== Summary ==
Alt text: A graphic announcing VRChat's Developer Update for 5 August 2022. There are two bullet point lists. One on the left is for released features, the list on the right is for features on the Live Beta.
Features released include: Horizon Adjust, Personal Mirror, Moveable Main Menu, Home Instance Type, Portal Prompt, Gesture Indicators, and a Particle Limiter
Features in Live Beta include: Earmuff Mode, Avatar Distance Hider, Mic Sensitivity, Mic Background Noise Remover, Keyboard Paste, Camera Near Clip Override, Personal Mirror Improvements

Source: https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-5-august-2022
